Joseph (IND) legally contests Rozier's (BOS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental and the leg contact by Rozier is marginal.

Young (IND) and Morris (BOS) engage legally before time expires. After the clock has expired, Morris appears to fall on his own accord and Young falls when resistance is removed, landing on Morris. Since time has expired, no foul can be called on either player. Event Assessments: CC = Correct Call, IC = Incorrect Call, CNC = Correct Non-Call, INC = Incorrect Non-Call
